(An American Werewolf In Paris)----(1997) The daughter of the werewolf from An American Werewolf in London is alive and living in Paris where her mother and stepfather are trying to overcome her lycanthropic disease. A trio of American tourists on a thrill-seeking trip around Europe manage to stop her from plunging to her death from the top of the Eiffel Tower and are embroiled in ahorrific but often hilarious plot involving a secret society of werewolves based in the city and a drug which allows them to change at any time. This time there's no need for a full moon.
